articles.title: Australia's Qube Holdings' shares jump 20% as Macquarie proposes $7.5 billion takeover deal - CNBC
articles.description: Macquarie has offered to acquire Qube for AU$5.2 in cash per share, representing a nearly 28% premium to Qube's closing level of AU$4.07 on Friday.
